lign-items: center;max-width: 90px;box-sizing: border-box;flex-shrink: 0;font-size: 0px;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"132\" style=\"margin: 0 auto;max-width: 100%;margin-right: auto;margin-left: auto;box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;border-style: none;display: block;border-radius: 4px;overflow-wrap: break-word;visibility: visible;width: 90px;\" data-imgfileid=\"100061855\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b5892876&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FINNfEriciaG5eqHJmgYUoq5H8qXcPxkfLiaZqKBCeZZqmWeKOrvibPRY9JChockAwuXyx52hpogmXqkwdQV0tH4v1g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"padding-top:8px;margin:0;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;padding-bottom:8px;font-size:15px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;word-wrap: break-word;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><span leaf=\"\">PodRocket：Angular v21 - 从 Signals 到测试，与 Mark Techson 对话</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- Paul 与 Mark Techson 坐下来深入解析 Angular v21。他们探讨了 Angular signals 如何驱动新功能如 Angular signal forms，提升可扩展性并简化状态管理。对话深入探讨了 Angular AI 工具，包括 Angular MCP 服务器、Angular AI 导师和 Angular Gemini CLI 扩展，解释了 Angular 如何适应现代 AI 优先的开发者工作流程。Mark 还分享了 Angular Aria 如何引入带有内置 Angular 可访问性的 Angular headless 组件，重塑 UX 协作。节目最后更新了在 Angular 中使用 Vitest 的情况，以及性能特性如 Angular defer 语法和 Angular 增量水合。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"padding:16px 20px;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.476px;display:flex;font-size:12px;border-color:rgb(62, 62, 62);box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;border-radius:6px;box-shadow:rgb(199, 201, 204) 0px 0px 0px inset;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;margin-to